1
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:15,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm Anna Akechi!
Mikuru started school today!</i></font>

2
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:18,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Legendary Pre-Kit charms from an old book!</i></font>

3
00:00:18,930 --> 00:00:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I went to deliver an umbrella and new
Pre-Kit to Mikuru at school, but...</i></font>

4
00:00:24,650 --> 00:00:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shouldn't bother Mikuru.</font>

5
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:34,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nijee turned the beloved school
swallow statue into Hannindas.</i></font>

6
00:00:35,820 --> 00:00:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We were out of step,
and Pochitan saved us.</i></font>

7
00:00:42,250 --> 00:00:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But we lost the Makoto Jewels.</i></font>

8
00:00:46,040 --> 00:00:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pochitan!</font>

9
00:00:48,540 --> 00:00:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">CURETTO DETECTIVE AGENCY</font>

10
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jett-senpai!</font>

11
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Pochitan, she's...</font>

12
00:01:00,890 --> 00:01:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's look for it
The hint is in the heart!</i></font>

13
00:01:00,890 --> 00:01:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>sagashi ni iku yo Heart ni Hint!</i></font>

14
00:01:04,810 --> 00:01:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A brilliant inspiration</i></font>

15
00:01:04,810 --> 00:01:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>rinto hirameku</i></font>

16
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure we'll find it
We're Precure, after all</i></font>

17
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>kitto mitsukeru
datte Precure</i></font>

18
00:01:10,940 --> 00:01:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's calling to us</i></font>

19
00:01:10,940 --> 00:01:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>watashitachi wo yondeiru</i></font>

20
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Where's the truth?
What will we discover?</i></font>

21
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>shinjitsu wa doko?
hakken wa nani?</i></font>

22
00:01:16,570 --> 00:01:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>One mystery after another</i></font>

23
00:01:16,570 --> 00:01:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>nazo ga nazo wo yondeiru</i></font>

24
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gather the pieces
From now to the past and future</i></font>

25
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>Puzzle wo atsume
genzai kara kako, mirai e</i></font>

26
00:01:26,330 --> 00:01:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like evidence
Something shining across time</i></font>

27
00:01:26,330 --> 00:01:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>shouko mitai ni
toki wo koe kagayaku mono</i></font>

28
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How? How? Is it a trick?</i></font>

29
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>nande? nande? Trick kana?</i></font>

30
00:01:34,550 --> 00:01:37,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why? Why? We'll face it</i></font>

31
00:01:34,550 --> 00:01:37,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>naze? naze? tachimukau</i></font>

32
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Look and feel
Figure out the secret</i></font>

33
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>mitsumete kanjite
himitsu wo tokiakasu no</i></font>

34
00:01:43,270 --> 00:01:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>One brave step will lead to a miracle</i></font>

35
00:01:43,270 --> 00:01:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>yuuki no ippo ga kiseki made michibiku</i></font>

36
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The answer?!
Found when you notice the unnoticed</i></font>

37
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>kotae!?
Kizuitenai mono ni kizuita toki</i></font>

38
00:01:54,570 --> 00:01:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's destiny, it's love
Whispered in a tiny voice</i></font>

39
00:01:54,570 --> 00:01:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>unmei ne tte daisuki yo tte
chicchana koe</i></font>

40
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:03,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's walk that road together!</i></font>

41
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:03,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>issho ni aruite ikou!</i></font>

42
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's look for it
The hint is in the heart!</i></font>

43
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>sagashi ni iku yo Heart ni Hint!</i></font>

44
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A brilliant inspiration</i></font>

45
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>rinto hirameku</i></font>

46
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The jewel key connects us
Opening the link moving forward</i></font>

47
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>Jewel no kagi ga tsunagaru
tsugi e no kizuna hiraku yo</i></font>

48
00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, us being born and having met
Is a wonderful mystery</i></font>

49
00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>nee umareta koto
meguri aeta koto no shinpi</i></font>

50
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:23,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Go on! Star Detective Precure!</i></font>

51
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:23,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>susume! Meitantei Precure!</i></font>

52
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Miraculous Pre-Kit Mirror Loupe!</i></font>

53
00:02:37,570 --> 00:02:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's drinking her milk, so don't worry.</font>

54
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two have a drink, too.</font>

55
00:02:46,330 --> 00:02:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When Pochitan started glowing,
this glowed too...?</font>

56
00:02:50,790 --> 00:02:53,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to investigate this further.</font>

57
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

58
00:02:55,630 --> 00:02:59,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I meant to give it to you, but I couldn't.</font>

59
00:03:04,010 --> 00:03:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Nijee? Why isn't he back?</font>

60
00:03:08,180 --> 00:03:10,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He even got two Makoto Jewels!</font>

61
00:03:11,100 --> 00:03:12,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's, like, totally bogus.</font>

62
00:03:14,820 --> 00:03:16,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cure Arcana Shadow.</font>

63
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go fetch Nijee.</font>

64
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lie lie, sir!</font>

65
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mikuru?</font>

66
00:03:32,540 --> 00:03:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to get the Makoto Jewels back.</font>

67
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Me too!
-You stay with Pochitan.</font>

68
00:03:42,220 --> 00:03:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I still hadn't figured out
how to carry it.</i></font>

69
00:03:46,350 --> 00:03:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then you helped me!</i></font>

70
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hanninda!</i></font>

71
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll turn it into swallows,
and transport it easily!</i></font>

72
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's my fault!</i></font>

73
00:04:06,530 --> 00:04:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just as my fortune-telling said.</font>

74
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're here.</font>

75
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you come back?</font>

76
00:04:18,670 --> 00:04:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get lost?</font>

77
00:04:20,130 --> 00:04:21,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not!</font>

78
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why?</font>

79
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:29,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want a more beautiful conclusion
for myself.</font>

80
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm actually a very greedy thief.</font>

81
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you going to do?</font>

82
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Defeat the Precures.</font>

83
00:04:43,530 --> 00:04:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like I told Maestro Usonoir!</font>

84
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no choice.</font>

85
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it with grace!</font>

86
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came back to look for evidence.</font>

87
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:08,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just as I expected.
I've been waiting, Detective.</font>

88
00:05:08,930 --> 00:05:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nijee!</font>

89
00:05:10,260 --> 00:05:13,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Calm down, baby!</font>

90
00:05:13,730 --> 00:05:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've just come to invite you
to a fabulous show!</font>

91
00:05:19,020 --> 00:05:23,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be able to see the Makoto Jewels,
by which I mean two swallows.</font>

92
00:05:23,530 --> 00:05:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

93
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:29,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The venue will be the town's
beautiful beach, Nijigahama.</i></font>

94
00:05:29,570 --> 00:05:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it romantic?</font>

95
00:05:33,620 --> 00:05:34,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

96
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:37,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be waiting for you there, baby!</font>

97
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still nothing.</font>

98
00:05:46,010 --> 00:05:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how I look into it,
I still can't figure it out.</font>

99
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Mikuru?</font>

100
00:05:51,850 --> 00:05:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She went to look for the Makoto Jewels.</font>

101
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:57,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsk. Leaving you and Pochitan behind.</font>

102
00:05:57,640 --> 00:06:00,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's... It's my fault.</font>

103
00:06:01,190 --> 00:06:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I couldn't talk to Mikuru.</font>

104
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anna?</font>

105
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was laughing with her friends.</font>

106
00:06:10,660 --> 00:06:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was a side of her I didn't know.</i></font>

107
00:06:13,370 --> 00:06:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's why...</i></font>

108
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mikuru has a world I know nothing about.</font>

109
00:06:19,210 --> 00:06:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We only just met, so it's not surprising.</font>

110
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't want to be a bother.</font>

111
00:06:26,010 --> 00:06:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I'd investigate alone.</font>

112
00:06:30,090 --> 00:06:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then we fought.</font>

113
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all reversed!</font>

114
00:06:38,810 --> 00:06:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

115
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:43,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like you and Mikuru
have switched places.</font>

116
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're thinking too much about Mikuru
and now you can't act, right?</font>

117
00:06:48,570 --> 00:06:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's like Mikuru.</i></font>

118
00:06:51,490 --> 00:06:54,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While Mikuru ran off on her own.</font>

119
00:06:54,910 --> 00:06:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's just like you.</i></font>

120
00:06:58,660 --> 00:07:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It means you're influencing each other.</font>

121
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even though you just met.</i></font>

122
00:07:04,670 --> 00:07:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can hardly believe it.</i></font>

123
00:07:10,010 --> 00:07:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you I only believe
what I see, right?</font>

124
00:07:13,470 --> 00:07:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has been a short time,
but I've seen you two, and I know.</font>

125
00:07:18,140 --> 00:07:23,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You are a fated, no, a miraculous pair.</i></font>

126
00:07:25,570 --> 00:07:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jett-senpai...</font>

127
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pochi?</font>

128
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pochitan...</font>

129
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave Pochitan with me!</font>

130
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:42,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go and find Mikuru.</font>

131
00:07:43,330 --> 00:07:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Together you're
Star Detective Precures, right?</font>

132
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jett-senpai...</font>

133
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pochi.</font>

134
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

135
00:07:55,970 --> 00:07:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be back!</font>

136
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Open!</font>

137
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:08,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pre-Kit Voice Memo!</font>

138
00:08:13,820 --> 00:08:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Anna?</i></font>

139
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mikuru! Where are you?</font>

140
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CURETTO DETECTIVE AGENCY</font>

141
00:08:17,530 --> 00:08:20,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm on my way to the beach!
Nijee told me to go there.</font>

142
00:08:21,710 --> 00:08:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go too!</font>

143
00:08:23,620 --> 00:08:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about Pochitan?</font>

144
00:08:24,870 --> 00:08:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry, Jett-senpai has her!</font>

145
00:08:24,870 --> 00:08:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CURETTO DETECTIVE AGENCY</font>

146
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be right there!</font>

147
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you call her here?</font>

148
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sea...</font>

149
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

150
00:08:41,060 --> 00:08:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She figured out my strategy?</i></font>

151
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

152
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, this will be a secret show,
not visible to Maestro Usonoir.</font>

153
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll defeat the Precures,
and take two Makoto Jewels back with me.</font>

154
00:08:58,660 --> 00:09:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Surprise!</font>

155
00:09:01,660 --> 00:09:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do as you like.</font>

156
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just hurry up and finish it.</font>

157
00:09:08,170 --> 00:09:11,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I plan to do anyway.</font>

158
00:09:16,470 --> 00:09:19,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been waiting, Precure.</font>

159
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Mikuru!
-Anna!</font>

160
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? The baby fairy isn't with you.</font>

161
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That suits me just fine.</font>

162
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

163
00:09:39,490 --> 00:09:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

164
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:49,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Open!</font>

165
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jewel Cure Watch!</font>

166
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:01,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Precure! Wake-up Time!</font>

167
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">3! Discover!</font>

168
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:18,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">6! And face one another!</font>

169
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">9! We are the miraculous duo!</font>

170
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spin Around!</font>

171
00:10:43,680 --> 00:10:45,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And finish off cutely!</font>

172
