00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

188
00:12:30,290 --> 00:12:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're good.</font>

189
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They made platforms?</font>

190
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:35,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Counterattack!</font>

191
00:12:47,220 --> 00:12:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Answer Attack!</font>

192
00:12:51,100 --> 00:12:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

193
00:12:53,890 --> 00:12:55,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

194
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mystique Reflection!</font>

195
00:13:08,490 --> 00:13:09,740
