199
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Han! Nin! Da!</font>

200
00:13:29,050 --> 00:13:30,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

201
00:13:33,810 --> 00:13:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sensing the Makoto Jewels?</font>

202
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:39,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to rest!</font>

203
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, fine! I'll take you to them.</font>

204
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone is so high-maintenance! Sheesh!</font>

205
00:13:52,330 --> 00:13:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Pre-Kit Mirror Loupes!</font>

206
00:13:54,660 --> 00:13:56,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want me to bring them?</font>

207
00:14:06,050 --> 00:14:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what working together looks like!</font>

208
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

209
00:14:25,940 --> 00:14:27,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like rain again.</font>

210
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's as if the sky
