211
00:14:34,490 --> 00:14:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to give you an umbrella.</font>

212
00:14:39,170 --> 00:14:39,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

213
00:14:40,420 --> 00:14:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I saw you with your friends.</font>

214
00:14:45,250 --> 00:14:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't want to bother you.</font>

215
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it made me realize...</font>

216
00:14:52,220 --> 00:14:57,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In this time, in this world,
