217
00:14:59,890 --> 00:15:03,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I investigated on my own.</font>

218
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

219
00:15:12,280 --> 00:15:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know.</font>

220
00:15:14,870 --> 00:15:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

221
00:15:16,910 --> 00:15:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You came to 1999 by yourself...
It must be lonely.</i></font>

222
00:15:24,290 --> 00:15:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You must've felt anxious.</i></font>

223
00:15:27,130 --> 00:15:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then...</i></font>

224
00:15:28,300 --> 00:15:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

225
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also acted on my own.</font>

226
00:15:37,310 --> 00:15:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

227
00:15:41,690 --> 00:15:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mystique.</font>

228
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:45,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

229
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's about time for this show to end!</font>

230
00:15:50,570 --> 00:15:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Precures!</font>

231
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time for your entrance?</font>

232
00:15:56,990 --> 00:15:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baby fairy.</font>

233
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I won't let you on stage!</font>

234
00:16:01,330 --> 00:16:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

235
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that?</font>

236
00:16:07,590 --> 00:16:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanted to deliver these, right?</font>

237
00:16:10,050 --> 00:16:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To Anna and Mikuru!</font>

238
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:16,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave this to me! Go! Pochitan!</font>

239
00:16:21,770 --> 00:16:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Star Detective Precures
have fairy friends who support them.</i></font>

240
00:16:26,060 --> 00:16:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They stand close to them,
and always watch over them.</i></font>

241
00:16:30,650 --> 00:16:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is Pochitan working hard to become theirs?</i></font>

242
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:37,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To become Answer
and Mystique's fairy friend!</i></font>

243
00:16:37,450 --> 00:16:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let you get in their way!
Bring it on!</font>

244
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Answer.</font>

245
00:17:10,570 --> 00:17:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mystique.</font>

246
00:17:13,650 --> 00:17:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's reversed.</font>

247
00:17:15,610 --> 00:17:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

248
00:17:16,990 --> 00:17:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jett-senpai said that.</font>

249
00:17:19,830 --> 00:17:22,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've swapped places since then.</font>

250
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:33,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Take a single step
and the answer will follow!</i></font>

251
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You taught me that.</font>

252
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A single step of courage
