253
00:17:43,020 --> 00:17:43,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

254
00:17:44,230 --> 00:17:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mystique.</font>

255
00:17:45,850 --> 00:17:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said I must be lonely and anxious
since I came to 1999.</font>

256
00:17:53,690 --> 00:17:55,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm okay now!</font>

257
00:17:55,650 --> 00:17:58,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She came to 1999?</i></font>

258
00:17:58,860 --> 00:18:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, I have you in my heart!</font>

259
00:18:04,250 --> 00:18:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! And I have you in my heart.</font>

260
00:18:08,870 --> 00:18:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are...</font>

261
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:12,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">not alone!</font>

262
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:17,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alone or together, I don't care!</font>

263
00:18:17,930 --> 00:18:19,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no future...</font>

264
00:18:20,260 --> 00:18:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">unless I defeat you!</font>

265
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Together with Mystique!</font>

266
00:18:24,390 --> 00:18:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Makoto Jewels!</font>

267
00:18:25,980 --> 00:18:27,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The swallow statue!</font>

268
00:18:28,060 --> 00:18:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll get them all back!</font>

269
00:18:34,570 --> 00:18:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just two! The three of us!</font>

270
00:18:47,250 --> 00:18:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Open!</font>

271
00:18:52,250 --> 00:18:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pre-Kit Mirror Loupe!</font>

272
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:55,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pochitan!</font>

273
00:19:02,220 --> 00:19:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makoto Jewel!</font>

274
00:19:11,770 --> 00:19:12,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look.</font>

275
00:19:14,570 --> 00:19:15,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feel.</font>

276
00:19:18,110 --> 00:19:19,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Solve the mystery!</font>

277
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is our answer!</font>

278
00:19:26,370 --> 00:19:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Precure! Flying Spectrum!</font>

279
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">CUREtto Case Closed!</font>

280
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanninda!</font>

281
00:19:57,020 --> 00:19:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pochi Pochi Cure Cure!</font>

282
00:20:10,830 --> 00:20:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go back.</font>

283
00:20:18,670 --> 00:20:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pochitan, I'm sorry.</font>

284
00:20:20,630 --> 00:20:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

285
00:20:24,930 --> 00:20:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Is everyone okay?</font>

286
00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jett-senpai!</font>

287
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you look at that,
