288
00:20:50,950 --> 00:20:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your role is finished.</font>

289
00:20:56,380 --> 00:20:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Maestro Usonoir.
-You may go.</font>

290
00:20:58,420 --> 00:21:00,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Maestro Usonoir.
-Down into the trap room.</font>

291
00:21:02,510 --> 00:21:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Maestro Usonoir.</font>

292
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Please, wait.</font>

293
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have some valuable intel.</font>

294
00:21:09,760 --> 00:21:14,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-One of the Precures, Cure Answer,
