295
00:21:15,060 --> 00:21:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

296
00:21:18,360 --> 00:21:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think she came from another time.</font>

297
00:21:21,610 --> 00:21:22,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

298
00:21:23,150 --> 00:21:27,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Precure who came from another time?</font>

299
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:30,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not written in the Tome of Mirages.</font>

300
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:32,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be...</font>

301
00:21:34,210 --> 00:21:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got in touch with my sister!</font>

302
00:21:36,790 --> 00:21:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said she was asleep
and missed the call!</font>

303
00:21:40,170 --> 00:21:42,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was midnight in London, after all.</i></font>

304
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was just like you said!</font>

305
00:21:45,760 --> 00:21:47,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CURETTO DETECTIVE AGENCY</font>

306
00:21:46,090 --> 00:21:47,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much!</font>

307
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:51,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad Keiko is alright, too!</font>

308
00:21:52,060 --> 00:21:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the swallow statue is back in place!</font>

309
00:21:55,810 --> 00:21:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-The ghost issue, too.
-Gold-star case closed!</font>

310
00:22:02,940 --> 00:22:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My candy!</font>

311
00:22:04,650 --> 00:22:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it out!</font>

312
00:22:07,280 --> 00:22:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give it back!</font>

313
00:22:09,450 --> 00:22:11,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, c'mon!</font>

314
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pochitan! Come down!</font>

315
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>(NaNaNaNa why? Why? WHY?
NaNaNaNa mystery? Mystery! ANSWER?!)</i></font>

316
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>(NaNaNaNa naze? naze? WHY?
NaNaNaNa nazo? nazo! ANSWER?!)</i></font>

317
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Connect the dots, oh? Oh my!</i></font>

318
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>ten to ten musundara ara? ara!</i></font>

319
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could it be a "gold-star case closed!"?
Could it?</i></font>

320
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>"hanamaru kaiketsu!" kana? kana?</i></font>

321
00:22:33,560 --> 00:22:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Reasoning turns around riddles
Twists and turns, reverse</i></font>

322
00:22:33,560 --> 00:22:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>suiri to nazo wa uragaeshi
niten santen gyakuten</i></font>

323
00:22:39,350 --> 00:22:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even words and behavior are traps? Traps!
Don't just believe them! No!</i></font>

324
00:22:39,350 --> 00:22:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>kotoba ya shigusa sae wana? wana!
unomi ni shite wa dame! dame!</i></font>

325
00:22:45,110 --> 00:22:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Pay attention, think and then
Take the first step!</i></font>

326
00:22:45,110 --> 00:22:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>yoku mite, kangaete, sorekara
fumidasu no yo ippo!</i></font>

327
00:22:50,910 --> 00:22:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I see someone in trouble
I immediately want to help</i></font>

328
00:22:50,910 --> 00:22:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>komatteiru hito mitara
sugu ni tasuketai</i></font>

329
00:22:56,700 --> 00:23:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cause I wanna, wanna do something
So I go running off</i></font>

330
00:22:56,700 --> 00:23:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>datte nantoka nantoka nantoka shitakute
kakedashiteiru</i></font>

331
00:23:01,630 --> 00:23:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Na Na Na mystery! Mystery!</i></font>

332
00:23:01,630 --> 00:23:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>Na Na Na nazo! nazo!</i></font>

333
00:23:03,540 --> 00:23:07,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Solving mysteries
Is what a Star Detective does</i></font>

334
00:23:03,540 --> 00:23:07,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>nazo wo toku no ga meitantei</i></font>

335
00:23:08,010 --> 00:23:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>See through lies and find truth
Find the answer for a smile</i></font>

336
00:23:08,010 --> 00:23:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>uso ka makoto ka mikiwamete
egao no kotae mitsukeru</i></font>

337
00:23:13,220 --> 00:23:19,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Na Na Na why? Why?
Together, I've got courage times 100</i></font>

338
00:23:13,220 --> 00:23:19,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>Na Na Na naze? naze?
minna to iru to yuuki 100 bai</i></font>

339
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Working together, we can figure it out
Friends are a true miracle</i></font>

340
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>chikara awasete norikoeru
tomo wa kiseki no katamari</i></font>

341
00:23:24,940 --> 00:23:27,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's go! Star Detective</i></font>

342
00:23:24,940 --> 00:23:27,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>iku yo! Meitantei</i></font>

343
00:23:27,740 --> 00:23:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Na Na Na why? Why?
Together, I've got courage times 1,000</i></font>

344
00:23:27,740 --> 00:23:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>Na Na Na naze? naze?
minna to iru to yuuki 1,000 bai</i></font>

345
00:23:33,990 --> 00:23:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hand in hand with my friends
Until everything's solved!</i></font>

